column2: SELECT o.objid, o.specobjid, o.ra, o.dec, pz.z, pz.zerr, pz.photoErrorClass, f.gain_u, f.gain_g, f.gain_r, f.gain_i, f.gain_z, f.saturationLevel_u , f.saturationLevel_g, f.saturationLevel_r, f.saturationLevel_i, f.saturationLevel_z From PhotoObjAll as o JOIN fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) AS n ON o.objid = n.objid JOIN Photoz AS pz ON n.objid = pz.objid JOIN Field AS f ON f.FieldID = o.FieldID WHERE o.type = # and pz.photoErrorClass IN () and pz.z > #e-# and pz.z < #
